    Introduction

    API aplikasi PAMPsi

    This documentation aims to provide all the information you need to work with our API.

    As you scroll, you'll see code examples for working with the API in different programming languages in the dark area to the right (or as part of the content on mobile). You can switch the language used with the tabs at the top right (or from the nav menu at the top left on mobile).

    Base URL

    http://localhost

    Authenticating requests

    This API is authenticated by sending an Authorization header with the value "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}".

    All authenticated endpoints are marked with a requires authentication badge in the documentation below.

    Anda harus login untuk mendapatkan token autentikasi

    Activity

    List Activity

    untuk list activity

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/admin/activity"
);

let params = {
    "fields[log_name]": "voluptas",
    "filter[log_name]": "et",
    "sort": "corporis",
    "page[number]": "6",
    "page[size]": "12",
    "include": "veniam",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

    Example response (401):

    
Unauthorized.
    Received response:
    Request failed with error:

    Request      

    GET admin/activity

    Query Parameters

    fields[log_name]  string optional  
    select kolom 'log_name','description','subject_type', 'subject_id','causer_type','causer_id','properties','created_at','updated_at'

    filter[log_name]  string optional  
    Filter by log_name.

    sort  string optional  
    sort data berdasarkan kolom. tambah tanda (-) untuk DESC.

    page[number]  integer optional  
    optional

    page[size]  integer optional  
    oprional

    include  string optional  
    get data relasi (dataUser).

    Request      

    GET admin/agenda

    Query Parameters

    fields[agenda]  string optional  
    select kolom 'nama_kategori','judul','deskripsi','lokasi','start_date','end_date','fasilitas' ,'pemater','poster','visible'

    filter[nama_kategori]  string optional  
    Filter by nama nama_kategori.

    sort  string optional  
    sort data berdasarkan kolom. tambah tanda (-) untuk DESC.

    page[number]  integer optional

    Create Agenda

    untuk create agenda

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/admin/agenda/create"
);

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "multipart/form-data",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

const body = new FormData();
body.append('nama_kategori', 'amet');
body.append('judul', 'numquam');
body.append('deskripsi', 'et');
body.append('lokasi', 'doloribus');
body.append('start_date', 'consequatur');
body.append('end_date', 'tenetur');
body.append('fasilitas', 'enim');
body.append('pemateri', 'aut');
body.append('objPoster', document.querySelector('input[name="objPoster"]').files[0]);

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body,
}).then(response => response.json());

    Example response (200):

    {
    "data": {
        "id": null,
        "nama_kategori": null,
        "judul": null,
        "deskripsi": null,
        "lokasi": null,
        "start_date": null,
        "end_date": null,
        "fasilitas": null,
        "pemateri": null,
        "poster": null
    }
}
    Received response:
    Request failed with error:

    Request      

    POST admin/agenda/create

    Body Parameters

    nama_kategori  string  

    judul  string  

    deskripsi  text optional  
    optional

    lokasi  string  

    start_date  dateTime  

    end_date  dateTime  

    fasilitas  string optional  
    optional

    pemateri  string  

    objPoster  file optional  
    optional

    Update Agenda

    untuk update agenda

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/admin/agenda/et/update"
);

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "multipart/form-data",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

const body = new FormData();
body.append('nama_kategori', 'quis');
body.append('judul', 'et');
body.append('deskripsi', 'quo');
body.append('lokasi', 'dolorem');
body.append('start_date', 'occaecati');
body.append('end_date', 'ex');
body.append('fasilitas', 'labore');
body.append('pemateri', 'corrupti');
body.append('objPoster', document.querySelector('input[name="objPoster"]').files[0]);

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body,
}).then(response => response.json());

    Example response (200):

    {
    "data": {
        "id": null,
        "nama_kategori": null,
        "judul": null,
        "deskripsi": null,
        "lokasi": null,
        "start_date": null,
        "end_date": null,
        "fasilitas": null,
        "pemateri": null,
        "poster": null
    }
}
    Received response:
    Request failed with error:

    Request      

    POST admin/agenda/{id}/update

    URL Parameters

    id  string  

    Body Parameters

    nama_kategori  string optional  
    optional

    judul  string optional  
    optional

    deskripsi  text optional  
    optional

    lokasi  string optional  
    optional

    start_date  dateTime optional  
    optional

    end_date  dateTime optional  
    optional

    fasilitas  string optional  
    optional

    pemateri  string optional  
    optional

    objPoster  file optional  
    optional

    Auth

    Login

    untuk login user

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/auth/login"
);

let headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "bmmrhdb2021!"
}

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

    Example response (200):

    {
    "status": "success",
    "message": "user berhasil login",
    "data": {
        "token": "token",
        "user": "user"
    }
}
    Received response:
    Request failed with error:

    Request      

    POST auth/login

    Body Parameters

    username  string optional  
    required.

    password  string optional  
    required.

    Logout

    untuk logout user

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(

);

    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

    "token": "est"
}

    body: JSON.stringify(body),

    Received response:

    Request      

    POST auth/logout

    Body Parameters

    Comment Forum

    View Comment Forum

    untuk view comment forum

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/user/forum/comment/18/view"
);

let params = {
    "fields[comment_forum]": "est",
    "filter[user_id]": "aspernatur",
    "sort": "architecto",
    "page[number]": "1",
    "page[size]": "15",
    "include": "ut",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

    Example response (401):

    
Unauthorized.
    Received response:
    Request failed with error:

    Request      

    GET user/forum/comment/{id}/view

    URL Parameters

    id  integer  
    id forum

    Query Parameters

    fields[comment_forum]  string optional  
    select kolom 'user_id','content','forum_id'

    filter[user_id]  string optional  
    Filter by nama 'user_id','content', 'forum_id'

    sort  string optional  
    sort data berdasarkan kolom. tambah tanda (-) untuk DESC.

    page[number]  integer optional  
    optional

    page[size]  integer optional  
    oprional

    include  string optional  
    get data relasi (dataUser).

    Create Comment Forum

    untuk create comment forum

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/user/forum/comment/eum/create"
);

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "content": "maiores"
}

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

    Example response (200):

    {
    "status": "success",
    "message": "Berhasil membuat komentar",
    "data": {
        "user_id": 3,
        "content": "halo",
        "commentable_type": "App\\Models\\Feed",
        "commentable_id": 1,
        "updated_at": "2021-02-27T02:38:11.000000Z",
        "created_at": "2021-02-27T02:38:11.000000Z",
        "id": 1
    }
}
    Received response:
    Request failed with error:

    Request      

    POST user/forum/comment/{id}/create

    URL Parameters

    id  string  

    Body Parameters

    content  string

    Comment

    View Comment

    untuk view comment

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/user/comment/19/view/ut"
);

let params = {
    "fields[comment]": "tempore",
    "filter[user_id]": "sint",
    "sort": "expedita",
    "page[number]": "2",
    "page[size]": "18",
    "include": "libero",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

    Example response (401):

    
Unauthorized.
    Received response:
    Request failed with error:

    Request      

    GET user/comment/{id}/view/{model}

    URL Parameters

    id  integer  
    id model

    model  string  
    nama model ex:'Feed','Artikel'

    Query Parameters

    fields[comment]  string optional  
    select kolom 'user_id','content','commentable_type','commentable_id'

    filter[user_id]  string optional  
    Filter by nama 'user_id','content','commentable_type','commentable_id'

    sort  string optional  
    sort data berdasarkan kolom. tambah tanda (-) untuk DESC.

    page[number]  integer optional  
    optional

    page[size]  integer optional  
    oprional

    include  string optional  
    get data relasi (dataUser).

    Create Forum

    untuk create forum

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/user/forum/create"
);

    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "multipart/form-data",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

const body = new FormData();
body.append('nama_kategori', 'alias');
body.append('judul', 'placeat');
body.append('isi', 'perspiciatis');
body.append('objImage', document.querySelector('input[name="objImage"]').files[0]);

    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body,
}).then(response => response.json());

    Create jurusan

    untuk create jurusan

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/admin/jurusan/create"
);

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "kode": "eum",
    "universitas_id": 16,
    "nama": "facere"
}

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

    Example response (200):

    
// respon berhasil disimpan
{
    "status": "success",
    "message": "data berhasil disimpan!",
    "data": {
        "id": 5,
        "kode": "KLI",
        "nama": "asdf",
        "dataUniversitas": {
            "id": 1,
            "nama": "Universitas Gajah Mada"
        }
    }
}

// respon validasi error
{
    "status": "failed",
    "message": "data gagal disimpan!",
    "data": {
        "errors": {
            "id": [
                "Kode Jurusan sudah digunakan!"
            ]
        }
    }
}
    Received response:
    Request failed with error:

    Request      

    POST admin/jurusan/create

    kode  string  
    kode jurusan

    universitas_id  integer  

    nama  string

    DataProvider Kota

    daftar collection kota dengan pagging

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/admin/all-kota"
);

let params = {
    "fields[kota]": "nesciunt",
    "filter[nama_kota]": "cupiditate",
    "filter[kode_kota]": "dolore",
    "filter[provinsi_id]": "ut",
    "sort": "similique",
    "page[number]": "7",
    "page[size]": "16",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

    select kolom 'nama_kategori','judul','isi','image','user_id','views'

    filter[nama]  string optional  
    Filter by 'nama_kategori','judul','isi','image','user_id','views'

    sort  string optional  
    sort data berdasarkan kolom. tambah tanda (-) untuk DESC.

    page[number]  integer optional  
    optional

    page[size]  integer optional  
    optional

    include  string optional  
    get data relasi (dataUser).

    Create Artikel

    untuk create artikel

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/user/artikel/create"
);

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "multipart/form-data",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

const body = new FormData();
body.append('nama_kategori', 'neque');
body.append('judul', 'iure');
body.append('isi', 'qui');
body.append('visible', 'neque');
body.append('objImage', document.querySelector('input[name="objImage"]').files[0]);

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body,
}).then(response => response.json());

    Example response (200):

    {
    "status": "success",
    "message": "data berhasil disimpan!",
    "data": {
        "id": 13,
        "kategori_id": "1",
        "judul": "judul13",
        "isi": "isi123",
        "image": null,
        "user_id": 1,
        "views": null,
        "created_at": "2021-02-24T02:59:17.000000Z",
        "updated_at": "2021-02-24T02:59:17.000000Z"
    }
}
    Received response:
    Request failed with error:

    Request      

    POST user/artikel/create

    Body Parameters

    nama_kategori  string  

    judul  string  

    isi  text  

    visible  enum  
    ('public','private')

    optional

    "Accept": "application/json",
};

    Negara

    DataProvider Negara

    daftar collection negara dengan pagging

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/admin/all-negara"
);

let params = {
    "fields[negara]": "enim",
    "filter[nama_negara]": "tenetur",
    "filter[kode_negara]": "sint",
    "sort": "dicta",
    "page[number]": "10",
    "page[size]": "12",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

    Create Provinsi

    untuk create provinsi

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/admin/provinsi/create"
);

    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "nama_provinsi": "expedita",
    "negara_id": 2,
    "kode_provinsi": "vitae"
}

    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

);

    "filter[username]": "enim",
    "filter[nama_lengkap]": "tempore",
    "filter[kota1_id]": "ea",
    "filter[kota2_id]": "molestiae",
    "filter[bidang_id]": "quidem",
    "filter[universitas_id]": "sunt",
    "sort": "enim",

};

    photo profile

    untuk upload foto profil

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/user/11/photo-profile"
);

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "multipart/form-data",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

const body = new FormData();
body.append('objPhoto', document.querySelector('input[name="objPhoto"]').files[0]);

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body,
}).then(response => response.json());

    update profile

    untuk update semua profil psikolog

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/user/11/profile"
);

    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "multipart/form-data",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

const body = new FormData();
body.append('email', 'sunt');
body.append('role_id', '10');
body.append('status', '2');
body.append('api_token', 'aliquid');
body.append('remember_token', 'quas');
body.append('nama_lengkap', 'nam');
body.append('tempat_lahir', 'laboriosam');
body.append('kota1_id', '9');
body.append('kota2_id', '19');
body.append('no_hp', '7');
body.append('jurusan_profesi', 'nobis');
body.append('tahun_masuk', '14');
body.append('tahun_lulus', '15');
body.append('nomor_ijazah', 'odit');
body.append('no_sipp', '7');
body.append('bidang_id', '19');
body.append('skill_kompetensi', 'ducimus');
body.append('profile_singkat', 'voluptatem');
body.append('longitude', 'nesciunt');
body.append('latitude', 'voluptatem');
body.append('jenis_kelamin', 'cum');
body.append('agama', 'ipsa');
body.append('layanan', 'quo');
body.append('photo_profile', document.querySelector('input[name="photo_profile"]').files[0]);

    method: "POST",
    headers,

}).then(response => response.json());

body.append('judul', 'repudiandae');
body.append('kota_id', '19');

body.append('end_date', 'ut');
body.append('objLogo', document.querySelector('input[name="objLogo"]').files[0]);

    List Vacancies

    untuk list vacancies

    requires authentication

    Example request:

    const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/user/vacancies"
);

let params = {
    "fields[agenda]": "ut",
    "filter[nama_kategori]": "voluptates",
    "sort": "consectetur",
    "page[number]": "11",
    "page[size]": "19",
    "include": "maiores",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

let headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

    Example response (401):

    
Unauthorized.
    Received response:
    Request failed with error:

    Request      

    GET user/vacancies

    Query Parameters

    fields[agenda]  string optional  
    select kolom 'perusahaan','judul','kota_id','nama_kategori', 'deskripsi','start_date','end_date','logo'

    filter[nama_kategori]  string optional  
    Filter by nama nama_kategori.

    sort  string optional  
    sort data berdasarkan kolom. tambah tanda (-) untuk DESC.

    page[number]  integer optional  
    optional

    page[size]  integer optional  
    oprional

    include  string optional  
    get data relasi (dataKota)
